        "file_path": "/workspace/answer.json",
        "old_string": "  \"text\": \"The k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object interface is the core abstraction for all Kubernetes API objects. It is defined in k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/interfaces.go and requires two methods: GetObjectKind() and DeepCopyObject().\\n\\nTypes in k8s.io/api/core/v1 implement runtime.Object by embedding two structs from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1: TypeMeta and ObjectMeta (or ListMeta for list types). TypeMeta provides the GetObjectKind() implementation through a receiver method defined in k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/meta.go. The DeepCopyObject() method is auto-generated by the deepcopy-gen code generator into zz_generated.deepcopy.go.\\n\\nKey files in the import chain:\\n\\n1. In k8s.io/api (api--v0.32.0):\\n   - core/v1/types.go: Defines all core API types (Pod, Service, Node, Secret, ConfigMap, Namespace, Event, PersistentVolume, PersistentVolumeClaim, ReplicationController, Binding, Endpoints, ResourceQuota, LimitRange, ServiceAccount, ComponentStatus, RangeAllocation, and their List variants, PodTemplate, and PodStatusResult) that implement runtime.Object by embedding metav1.TypeMeta and metav1.ObjectMeta/ListMeta.\\n   - core/v1/register.go: Registers these types into runtime.Scheme via the addKnownTypes function, which calls scheme.AddKnownTypes(SchemeGroupVersion, &Pod{}, &PodList{}, ...). This imports runtime from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime and metav1 from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1.\\n   - core/v1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go: Auto-generated file containing DeepCopyObject() method implementations for all registered types, enabling each type to satisfy the Object interface.\\n\\n2. In k8s.io/apimachinery (kubernetes--v1.32.0/staging/src/k8s.io/apimachinery):\\n   - pkg/runtime/interfaces.go (lines 336-339): Defines the Object interface with GetObjectKind() and DeepCopyObject() methods.\\n   - pkg/apis/meta/v1/types.go (lines 42 and 111): Defines the TypeMeta and ObjectMeta struct types that are embedded by all core/v1 types.\\n   - pkg/apis/meta/v1/meta.go (line 117): Provides the GetObjectKind() implementation for TypeMeta: `func (obj *TypeMeta) GetObjectKind() schema.ObjectKind { return obj }`.\\n   - pkg/runtime/schema/interfaces.go: Defines the ObjectKind interface used by GetObjectKind().\\n\\nThe import chain flows from core/v1 types through metav1 to the runtime.Object interface definition. The go.mod in k8s.io/api specifies the dependency: k8s.io/apimachinery v0.32.0. All 28 types in core/v1 that embed both TypeMeta and ObjectMeta are registered in core/v1/register.go and implement runtime.Object, making them compatible with Kubernetes serialization, storage, and API machinery.\"",
        "new_string": "  \"text\": \"The k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object interface is the core abstraction for all Kubernetes API objects. It is defined in k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/interfaces.go (lines 336-339) and requires two methods: GetObjectKind() schema.ObjectKind and DeepCopyObject() Object.\\n\\nImport Chain and Type Implementation:\\nTypes in k8s.io/api/core/v1 implement runtime.Object by embedding two structs from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1: TypeMeta and ObjectMeta (or ListMeta for list types). TypeMeta provides the GetObjectKind() implementation through a receiver method defined in k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/meta.go (line 117): `func (obj *TypeMeta) GetObjectKind() schema.ObjectKind { return obj }`. The DeepCopyObject() method is auto-generated by the deepcopy-gen code generator and placed in zz_generated.deepcopy.go.\\n\\nCore/v1 Types Implementing runtime.Object (37 total):\\nSingle object types: Binding, ComponentStatus, ConfigMap, Endpoints, Event, LimitRange, Namespace, Node, PersistentVolume, PersistentVolumeClaim, Pod, PodStatusResult, PodTemplate, RangeAllocation, ReplicationController, ResourceQuota, Secret, Service, ServiceAccount.\\nList types: ComponentStatusList, ConfigMapList, EndpointsList, EventList, LimitRangeList, NamespaceList, NodeList, PersistentVolumeClaimList, PersistentVolumeList, PodList, PodTemplateList, ReplicationControllerList, ResourceQuotaList, SecretList, ServiceAccountList, ServiceList.\\nSpecial type: SerializedReference.\\n\\nKey Files in Import Chain:\\n\\n1. k8s.io/api Repository (api--v0.32.0):\\n   - core/v1/types.go: Defines all 37 core API types that implement runtime.Object by embedding metav1.TypeMeta and metav1.ObjectMeta (or ListMeta for list types). Imports metav1 from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1.\\n   - core/v1/register.go: Registers these types into runtime.Scheme via the addKnownTypes function. Uses runtime.NewSchemeBuilder to create SchemeBuilder and calls scheme.